{"word":"G3354 - μετρέω - metréō - met-reh'-o - Figuratively","slug":"G3354","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μετρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>metréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>met-reh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Figuratively"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - metreo&#x0304;</b> - <i>met-reh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3358\">G3358</a>; to <i>measure</i> (that is, ascertain in size by a fixed standard); by implication to <i>admeasure</i> (that is, allot by rule); figuratively to <i>estimate:</i> - measure, mete."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G280\">G280</a>, <a href=\"#/G3357\">G3357</a>, <a href=\"#/G3358\">G3358</a>"}]}